{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>死者73歲姓劉，警方正就事件展開調查。現場消息稱，死者是泳客。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126444497828319232871596.jpeg/UCbcJ3mfhY87q4GGSJvDXpGqyPY3OHx82DQXDtg0Fw4\" alt=\"大埔龍尾泳灘有男子遇溺身亡。（讀者提供）\"><figcaption>大埔龍尾泳灘有男子遇溺身亡。（讀者提供）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126445282238664704450291.jpeg/X0Klr6TrIBVTUqT9QSjEHWOoIC3BFAAraTmVOGk5lTg\" alt=\"七旬翁在沙灘疑遇溺，送院不治。（讀者提供）\"><figcaption>七旬翁在沙灘疑遇溺，送院不治。（讀者提供）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126434998862221312094258.jpeg/b8yHi40lMVkzZgzwbxf7Joq3WND3rxoWLqrSHS6q0h0\" alt=\"男子被送到那打素醫院搶救。（資料圖片）\"><figcaption>男子被送到那打素醫院搶救。（資料圖片）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-30T01:25:31.277275+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":94,"images":3,"source":"HK01 突發","fallback":"none"}}